y disks with its\nsimultaneous coverage of the full H and K bands with high spectral resolution\n($R$= 45,000) allowing many aspects of the sources to be investigated at once.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2016 02:17:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-17"}
