ity, with a possible\nflare-like or microlensing-like event. Conclusions: All of these results came\nonly from the photometric observations of the systems and can be considered as\na good starting point for future dedicated observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2016 07:40:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
