ree\nabsorbed by a circumnuclear photo-ionized region, and self-absorbed nonthermal\nsynchrotron from disk corona, as the origin of the high-frequency excess\ncomponent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2016 15:58:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
